title: Install Org-Transclusion in Doom Emacs
tags: @zettel _method doomemacs orgmode
roam-id: 23a9a1ab-9ee4-42ee-bcc6-ea09b12ea4be
type: text/markdown

``` elisp
;; ~/.doom.d/package.el
(package! org-transclusion)
```

``` elisp
;; ~/.doom.d/config.el
(use-package! org-transclusion
  :after org
  :init
  (map!
   :map global-map "<f12>" #'org-transclusion-add
   :leader
   :prefix "n"
   :desc "Org Transclusion Mode" "t" #'org-transclusion-mode))
```
